<plot>Chester and Doreen Barnes seem like any ordinary couple. The thing is that they are not! Chester is an aging Superhero Captain Miracle who has hung up his cape. However, the normal humdrum inertia of their retired lives is constantly under threat from Dr Nightshade, Captain Miracle's age-old nemesis. The question is whether Captain Miracle will answer Nightshade's challenge and fly one last time?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?612313</url></doc>
